callback.description:
Open this URL in browser and log in:

{authorization_url}

After login, copy the full URL from the browser address bar and paste it below. Supported callback formats: https://www.compraonline.bonpreuesclat.cat/sso-login?... or bonpreu-atm://login?... Redirect URI used for token exchange: {redirect_uri}. Authorization codes are one-time use; if exchange fails, restart login to get a fresh callback URL.
